description:
Live Show Mondays brings you the conclusion of the April live show that featured Felony, Darling, and sexy co-top Isis Love.
Well what happens when you're live and things go wrong? If it's a studio shoot, it's edited out. If it's live it's right there for everyone to see. Not everything always goes perfect. Sometimes it just doesn't work out...
